- **Pro card** has a subtle green-tinted background + green border, standing out without being gaudy
- **Hover states:** Cards lift with `translateY(-5px)`, regular cards brighten their border, featured card gets a dual-ring glow; CTA buttons shift color and cast a shadow
- **Billing toggle:** Pill-style switcher; annual selection shows inline `−20%` badge; price updates live
